           README FOR JAVAPATHFINDER BUILD-TOOLS

this archive contains the third-party tools that are required to build
Java PathFinder, which at this point are

 - Ant >= 1.7alpha : http://ant.apache.org
 - JUnit >= 4.1    : http://www.junit.org

See the "Prerequisites" section in the documentation or the README for
details.

Ant is distributed under the Apache license, and JUnit under the Common Public
License (CPL). The JUnit license and sources can be found in the
build-tools/junit directory.
